This frontend web application was build with Vue 3

Tech Stack

 - Vue 3
 - Vite
 - JavaScript
 - HTML5 & CSS3
 - npm

-------------------------------------------------

Project Setup

Install dependencies
 > npm install

Run development server
 > npm run dev

The app will be available at: http://localhost:5173

-------------------------------------------------

Project Structure

   src/
    ├─ assets/        -> css file
    ├─ components/    x
    ├─ views/         -> desktop and mobile pages
    ├─ router/        -> Router config
    ├─ services/      -> WebSockets
    ├─ App.vue        -> Root component
    └─ main.js        -> Application entry point